{"tid":2209630,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"SSD NAND同NEME有咩分別","createTime":"2020-09-19T18:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T17:06:45.000Z","uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f45844b2a677f2b90b19bc8be36c3626ac38cf09","tid":2209630,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPhqa3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPhqa3s.png&h=56ae52dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的！我今日去買SSD，見到兩款睇落差唔多，咪買貴幾十蚊果款囉，但返屋企google下d測試，原來貴果款慢幾倍，得五分一速度？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪中左伏，我見間間都咁上下價，點解會咁定價？"},{"pid":"1a1391d4498ab41afd6fa14a17f1f6028e4e4475","tid":2209630,"uid":174432,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"SATA M.2都買得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cce8a50f3dfbfa9ecf1921132e98a97b8b6db8","tid":2209630,"uid":209738,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"NVMe SSD 的讀寫速度快過M. 2 SATA SSD<br />\n<br />\nM. 2 SATA SSD的讀寫速度最快在550MB/s左右<br />\nM. 2 NVMe  SSD的讀寫速度容易超越1000MB/s<br />\n<br />\nM. 2 NVMe SSD是比較新穎的產品，假如你想買它，我建議你先檢查你的底板是否兼容它。"},{"pid":"ac55b9a43246d3678e44a3c753b59cdd722935ca","tid":2209630,"uid":375370,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"1.下面果款係上面果款的迭代升級，上款的B/B&amp;M key走sata類型SSD所有廠商應該己停產，是商戶庫存貨。<br />\r\n2.睇黎樓主買到番屋企先番轉頭做買之前就應該要做既功課，電子野買之前唔做好功課永遠係大罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n3.現在對第一款有須求的大約是4至6年的筆記本，佢地會有啲有限定B/B&amp;M key M.2 的接口，想升空間只能食死第一款sata B/B&amp;M M.2 SSD 買一條少一條有理由抬價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n4.3只是抬價理由之一，商家清庫存梗係想有幾快得幾快，過時商品抬高價亦都係想摸啲相信一分錢一分貨而且又唔撚做功課既水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d2d207e8ddef0e4d966cd9dc07be6a49cd0add","tid":2209630,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score